OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FThe court heard Jones visited Ms
OL,7,FEvans' home in Bigyn Road, Llanelli,
OL,8,Fat 9:19 am on 5 July, 2024.
OL,10,FHe was recorded on a doorbell camera
OL,11,Ftalking on the phone with Sophie
OL,12,Fbefore she opened the front door to
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FHe was inside the house for just 40
OL,16,Fminutes before CCTV captured him
OL,17,Frunning back to his car, returning to
OL,18,Fthe house and then driving off.
