OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FIn the moments before, he had attacked
OL,7,FSophie and left her for dead in her
OL,8,Fkitchen.
OL,10,FFollowing the incident, CCTV spotted
OL,11,FJones driving to Llanelli town centre
OL,12,Fwhere he went to a bank and a bakery
OL,13,Fbefore going home to Burry Port.
OL,15,FBy 10:35 am he had left his home
OL,16,Faddress by car and drove to Pembrey
OL,17,FCountry Park.
