OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FJones had sent several text to his ex-
OL,7,Fpartner telling them he thought he had
OL,8,Fbeen "scammed" and that he "won't be
OL,9,Fabout."
OL,11,FHe had suspected Sophie and his son
OL,12,FJamie Davies of trying to defraud him.
OL,14,FAt 5:27 pm, police received a 999-call
OL,15,Freporting that Richard Jones had
OL,16,Fkilled Sophie Evans.
OL,18,FOfficers immediately attended her
OL,19,Faddress and forced entry through the
OL,20,Fback door.
