OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FSophie's body was discovered on the
OL,7,Fkitchen floor and was confirmed dead.
OL,9,FFifteen minutes later, Jones texted
OL,10,Fhis ex-partner asking her not to say
OL,11,Fanything.
OL,13,FFollowing police enquiries, Jones was
OL,14,Ffound by officers near the entrance to
OL,15,FPembrey Country Park at 8pm.
OL,17,FHe was arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,18,Fand taken to hospital where he
OL,19,Fremained for four days.
