OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FWhen he arrived in custody on 9 July,
OL,7,F2024, Jones made a phone call to his
OL,8,Fmother in which he told her he had
OL,9,F"messed up again."
OL,11,FOfficers found handwritten notes by
OL,12,FJones saying, "I got scammed and
OL,13,Frinsed by my own son, so I dealt with
OL,14,Fit myself, I had no other choice."
OL,16,FOn 11 July, he was charged with the
OL,17,Fmurder of Sophie Evans.
