OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Gareth
OL,7,FRoberts said: "The guilty verdict of
OL,8,Fthe court is welcomed. Our thoughts at
OL,9,Fthis time are with Sophie and the
OL,10,Ffamily and friends who loved her.
OL,12,F"Sophie was a young mother, beloved
OL,13,Ffamily member and friend. Richard
OL,14,FJones has been found guilty of what
OL,15,Fwas a senseless, cowardly act
OL,16,Ftriggered by anger and temper.
