OL,6,F"Sophie was within her own home and
OL,7,Fnot in a position to defend herself
OL,8,Ffrom Richard Jones' cruel act of
OL,9,Fviolence. The family will take some
OL,10,Fcomfort that he's now removed from
OL,11,Fsociety and cannot harm any others."
OL,13,FJones will appear in court on 3 March
OL,14,Ffor sentencing.
